OL,7,FThe British Rally Championships have
OL,8,Fpaid tribute to competitor Dai Roberts
OL,9,Fwho died in a crash, saying "his
OL,10,Fincredible legacy" will live on across
OL,11,F"every car for years to come".
OL,13,FCo-driver Dai Roberts, from Carmarthen
OL,14,Fin south Wales, died after the
OL,15,Fincident on the Edrom Mains road, near
OL,16,FDuns, before 11am on 24 May 2025.
OL,18,FRally driver James Williams was taken
OL,19,Fto hospital with serious injuries.
OL,20,FPolice Scotland confirmed that no one
OL,21,Felse was injured in the incident.
