OL,7,FThe organisation said the 39-year-old
OL,8,F"touched everyone who had the
OL,9,Fprivilege of working alongside him."
OL,11,FIn a statement, they said: "Hailing
OL,12,Ffrom his beloved Carmarthen, he was a
OL,13,Fman deeply rooted in the sport, with a
OL,14,Fcareer spanning over 22 years at both
OL,15,Fnational and international levels.
OL,17,F"His partnership with several talented
OL,18,Fdrivers, including James Williams in
OL,19,Frecent seasons, was built not only on
OL,20,Fskill but on unwavering trust.
