OL,7,F"Dai knew all too well the fragility
OL,8,Fof life in motorsport, yet, despite
OL,9,Fsuch heartbreak, he continued, his
OL,10,Flove for rallying never dimmed, and
OL,11,Fneither did his strength.
OL,13,F"He is survived by his family,
OL,14,Fincluding his wife Louise and
OL,15,Fchildren, who were the centre of his
OL,16,Fworld.
