OL,7,F"They and the wider rallying community
OL,8,Fcontinue to grieve not only for a
OL,9,Fcompetitor, but a man who lived with
OL,10,Ffire in his belly, gave generously,
OL,11,Fand left the sport better than he
OL,12,Ffound it.
OL,14,F"Dai Roberts was, simply put, one of
OL,15,Frallying's good souls. His ferocious
OL,16,Fpassion on the stages and quick wit
OL,17,Fand humour away from them will live on
OL,18,Fwith his incredible legacy that will
OL,19,Froll out the service park with every
OL,20,Fcar for years to come."
