OL,7,FThe motorsport group say they will
OL,8,Fhonour the welshman's legacy in future
OL,9,Fevents.
OL,11,FMotorsport UK, the sport's governing
OL,12,Fbody, are conducting a "full
OL,13,Finvestigation" into the circumstances
OL,14,Fof Dai's death.
OL,16,FIn a statement last weekend, the group
OL,17,Fsaid: "Motorsport UK sends its
OL,18,Fcondolences to Dai's family and
OL,19,Ffriends, the Jim Clark Rally, Jim
OL,20,FClark Memorial Motor Club and members
OL,21,Fof the motorsport community."
